  "page": "Yin",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Henrik-zahringer-unseenwesteros-yiti-gate.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/29/Henrik-zahringer-unseenwesteros-yiti-gate.jpg/300px-Henrik-zahringer-unseenwesteros-yiti-gate.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/29/Henrik-zahringer-unseenwesteros-yiti-gate.jpg/450px-Henrik-zahringer-unseenwesteros-yiti-gate.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/29/Henrik-zahringer-unseenwesteros-yiti-gate.jpg/600px-Henrik-zahringer-unseenwesteros-yiti-gate.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Henrik-zahringer-unseenwesteros-yiti-gate.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Yin, artwork by Henrik Zahringer.</div></div></div>\n<p><b>Yin</b> is the great port city of <a href=\"/index.php/Yi_Ti\" title=\"Yi Ti\">Yi Ti</a> on the <a href=\"/index.php/Jade_Sea\" title=\"Jade Sea\">Jade Sea</a>. It is connected by a trade route to <a href=\"/index.php/Asabhad\" title=\"Asabhad\">Asabhad</a> to the northwest. A river from the forests of Yi Ti leads south to Yin.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtloiaf_the_east.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtloiaf_the_east.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>The dynasties of the <a href=\"/index.php/Grey_emperors\" title=\"Grey emperors\">grey</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Indigo_emperors\" title=\"Indigo emperors\">indigo</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Pearl-white_emperors\" title=\"Pearl-white emperors\">pearl-white emperors</a> ruled the <a href=\"/index.php/Golden_Empire_of_Yi_Ti\" title=\"Golden Empire of Yi Ti\">Golden Empire of Yi Ti</a> from their seats at Yin, and, in the present, the <a href=\"/index.php/Azure_emperors\" title=\"Azure emperors\">azure emperors</a> have done the same.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_bones_and_beyond:_yi_ti.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_bones_and_beyond:_yi_ti.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Yin&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtloiaf_the_east.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtloiaf_the_east.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Lands_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"The Lands of Ice and Fire\">The Lands of Ice and Fire</a></i>,  The East.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_bones_and_beyond:_yi_ti.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_bones_and_beyond:_yi_ti.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Bones and Beyond: Yi Ti.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403193534\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.019 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.020 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 157/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8574/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 605/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 207/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/2